  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine if Zonisamide is effective in reducing tremors in
      patients with Essential Tremor.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The subjects will remain on their usual medication and a baseline assessment using the Fahn
      Tolosa Marin tremor rating scale will be performed and will be video taped.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
